## 2. Test Summary

**Purpose:**  
To verify that selected Java controller classes within the application behaved correctly in isolation using JUnit testing.

**Scope:**  
This testing covered:

- HomeController home page view return behaviour
- HomeController word of the day model attribute behaviour when nouns existed
- HomeController behaviour when no nouns were available

