## 3. System Overview

This document recorded the JUnit testing carried out on selected controller classes within the application. The testing focused on confirming that controller methods returned the correct view name, that model attributes were added only where expected, and that dependent repository behaviour could be isolated using mocks. The HomeController tests verified that the home page returned the correct view, that a word of the day was added to the model when noun data was available, and that no word of the day attribute was added when the repository returned no nouns.

