## 8. Test Cases

This section recorded the unit testing completed against selected Java controller classes using JUnit and Mockito.

### 8.1 HomeController Class

| Test ID | Class Under Test | Test Method | Description | Expected Result | Actual Result | Status |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| JUT-CON-001 | HomeController.java | home_ShouldReturnIndexView | Verify that the home controller method returns the correct home page view name | The method returns `index` | `index` was returned | Passed |
| JUT-CON-002 | HomeController.java | home_ShouldAddWordOfTheDay_WhenNounsExist | Verify that the controller adds a `wordOfTheDay` attribute to the model when noun data exists | The method returns `index` and the model receives the `wordOfTheDay` attribute | `index` was returned and the `wordOfTheDay` attribute was added correctly | Passed |
| JUT-CON-003 | HomeController.java | home_ShouldNotAddWordOfTheDay_WhenNoNounsExist | Verify that the controller does not add a `wordOfTheDay` attribute when no nouns are available | The method returns `index` and no `wordOfTheDay` attribute is added to the model | `index` was returned and no `wordOfTheDay` attribute was added | Passed |

